            "id": "https://liuhuo23.github.io/2022/02/11/linux/shell%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/",
            "url": "https://liuhuo23.github.io/2022/02/11/linux/shell%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC/",
            "title": "shell脚本",
            "date_published": "2022-02-11T02:43:46.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"一-shell-基础结构\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#一-shell-基础结构\">#</a> 一 shell 基础结构</h1>\n<h2 id=\"1标准来说shell脚本分为三部分\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#1标准来说shell脚本分为三部分\">#</a> <strong>1. 标准来说，shell 脚本分为三部分</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>第一部分：\n<ul>\n<li>脚本第一行： 魔法字符 #！ 指定解释器【必写】</li>\n<li>#！/bin/bash 表示以下内容使用 bash 解释器解析</li>\n<li><mark>注意</mark>  如果直接将解释器路径写死在脚本里，可能在默写系统就会存在找不到解释器的兼容性问题。所以可以使用： #！/bin/env #！/bin/env bash</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>第二部分：\n<ul>\n<li>注释号（#） 说明，对脚本的基本信息进行描述</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>第三部分：\n<ul>\n<li>脚本要实现的具体代码内容</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"二-shell两种运行方式\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#二-shell两种运行方式\">#</a> 二 shell 两种运行方式</h1>\n<h2 id=\"1-标准脚本执行方法\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#1-标准脚本执行方法\">#</a> 1.  标准脚本执行方法</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><figcaption data-lang=\"Bash\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">chmod</span> <span class=\"token number\">755</span> *.sh  <span class=\"token comment\"># 赋予脚本文件可执行权限</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>./shell.sh <span class=\"token comment\"># 运行脚本</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id=\"2-非标准执行方法\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#2-非标准执行方法\">#</a> 2. 非标准执行方法</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code>bash shell.sh</code></li>\n<li><code>sh shell.sh</code></li>\n<li><code>source shell.sh</code></li>\n<li><code>bash -x shell .sh</code>\n<ul>\n<li>-x : 一般用于排错，查看脚本的执行过程</li>\n<li>-n： 用来查看脚本的语法是否由问题</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"shell脚本基本语法\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#shell脚本基本语法\">#</a> shell 脚本基本语法</h1>\n<h2 id=\"1变量名规则\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#1变量名规则\">#</a> 1. 变量名规则</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>变量名由字符串，下划线，数字 三种组成，且数字不能开头</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2变量的分类\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#2变量的分类\">#</a> 2. 变量的分类</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>本地变量： 当前用户自定义的变量。当前进程中有效，其他进程给及当前进程的子进程无效</li>\n<li>环境变量： 当前进程有效，并且能够被子进程调用\n<ul>\n<li>env： 环境变量</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"3-数组\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#3-数组\">#</a> 3. 数组</h2>\n<h3 id=\"31-数组的分类\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#31-数组的分类\">#</a> 3.1 数组的分类：</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>普通数组： 只能使用整数作为数组索引（元素的下标）</li>\n<li>关联数组： 可以使用字符串作为数组索引（元素的下标）</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"32-创建数组\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#32-创建数组\">#</a> 3.2 创建数组</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>一次赋予一个值</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><figcaption data-lang=\"Bash\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><ul>\n<li>\n<p>一次赋予多个值</p>\n<p>数组名 =（值 1 值 2 值 3）</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><figcaption data-lang=\"Bash\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">nums</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span> <span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h1 id=\"shell-实例\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#shell-实例\">#</a> shell 实例</h1>\n<h2 id=\"1搜索子域名的shell脚本\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#1搜索子域名的shell脚本\">#</a> 1. 搜索子域名的 shell 脚本</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><figcaption data-lang=\"Bash\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">#！/bin/bash</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">wget</span> www.megacorpone.com</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">grep</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"href=\"</span> index.html <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">awk</span> -F <span class=\"token string\">\"http://\"</span> <span class=\"token string\">'{print $2}'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">cut</span> -d <span class=\"token string\">\"/\"</span> -f <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">cut</span> -d <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\&quot;\">\\\"</span>\"</span> -f <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> url.txt</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token for-or-select variable\">url</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">`</span><span class=\"token function\">cat</span> url.txt<span class=\"token variable\">`</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">do</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre>  <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">name</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">host</span>  $url <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">cut</span> -d <span class=\"token string\">\" \"</span> -f <span class=\"token number\">4</span> <span class=\"token operator\"><span class=\"token file-descriptor important\">1</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"token file-descriptor important\">&amp;2</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre>  <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$url</span>  <span class=\"token variable\">$name</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">done</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id=\"2嗅探并抓去网页快照shell脚本\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#2嗅探并抓去网页快照shell脚本\">#</a> 2. 嗅探并抓去网页快照 shell 脚本</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><figcaption data-lang=\"Bash\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token shebang important\">#!/bin/bash</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>nmap -A -p <span class=\"token number\">80</span> --open <span class=\"token number\">10.11</span>.1.0/24 -OG nmap_scan_url</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">cat</span> nmap_scan_url <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">grep</span> <span class=\"token number\">80</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">grep</span> -v <span class=\"token string\">\"nmap\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">awk</span> <span class=\"token string\">'{print &amp;2}'</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token for-or-select variable\">ip</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">cat</span> namp_scan_url <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">grep</span> <span class=\"token number\">80</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">grep</span> -v <span class=\"token string\">\"nmap\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">awk</span> <span class=\"token string\">'{print $2}'</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">do</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">url</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\">$ip</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre>\t<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">out</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\">$ip</span>.png</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">done</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"9\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;html&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;br&gt;\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> web.html</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"10\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">ls</span> -l *.png <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">awk</span> -F <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'{print $1\":\\n&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=\\\"\"$1\"\"$2\"\\\" width=600&gt;&lt;br&gt;\"}'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&gt;&gt;</span> web.html</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"11\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&gt;&gt;</span>web.html</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>3. 漏洞利用程序下载脚本</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><figcaption data-lang=\"Bash\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>Searchsploit 是一个针对ExploitDB的命令行搜索工具，他允许我们随时随地获取Exploit数据库的脱机副本</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>● -w 返回https://www.exploit_db.com上的信息</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>● -t 搜索漏洞利用标题</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre>searchsploit afd windows -w -t</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre>searchsploit afd windows -w -t <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">grep</span> http <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">cut</span> -f <span class=\"token number\">2</span> -d <span class=\"token string\">\"|\"</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token for-or-select variable\">e</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span>searchsploit afd windows -w -t <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">grep</span> http <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">cut</span> -f <span class=\"token number\">2</span> -d <span class=\"token string\">\"|\"</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">do</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">exp_name</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> $e <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">cut</span> -d <span class=\"token string\">\"/\"</span> -f <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> url <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> $e <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sed</span> <span class=\"token string\">'s/exploit/raw/'</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class=\"token function\">wget</span> -q --no-check-certificate <span class=\"token variable\">$url</span> -O <span class=\"token variable\">$exp_name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token keyword\">done</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token number\">4</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">#!/bin/bash</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"9\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token for-or-select variable\">e</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span>searchsploit afd windows -w -t <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">grep</span> http <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">cut</span> -f <span class=\"token number\">2</span> -d <span class=\"token string\">\"|\"</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"10\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">do</span> </pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"11\"></td><td><pre> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">exp_name</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> $e <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">cut</span> -d <span class=\"token string\">\"/\"</span> -f <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"12\"></td><td><pre> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">url</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">echo</span> $e <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">sed</span> <span class=\"token string\">'s/exploit/raw/'</span><span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"13\"></td><td><pre> <span class=\"token function\">wget</span> -q --no-check-certificate <span class=\"token variable\">$url</span> -O <span class=\"token variable\">$exp_name</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"14\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">done</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li>\n</ul>\n",
            "tags": [
                "linux"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://liuhuo23.github.io/2022/02/10/linux/centos7%20%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/",
            "url": "https://liuhuo23.github.io/2022/02/10/linux/centos7%20%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/",
            "title": "centos7配置服务器",
            "date_published": "2022-02-10T10:43:46.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"web服务器搭建\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#web服务器搭建\">#</a> web 服务器搭建</h1>\n<h2 id=\"11-lamp\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#11-lamp\">#</a> 1.1 LAMP</h2>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/liuhuo23/blog-img/main/img/lamp.png\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>L --&gt; linux【操作系统】</li>\n<li>A --&gt; Apache 【中间件】</li>\n<li>M ---&gt; MySQL,MariaDB 【数据管理系统】</li>\n<li>P --&gt; PHP/Perl/Python 【脚本语言】</li>\n</ul>\n<p><mark>注意：</mark> 以下命令必须用 root 权限</p>\n<h3 id=\"步骤一-安装-apache组件\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#步骤一-安装-apache组件\">#</a> 步骤一： 安装 Apache 组件</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><figcaption data-lang=\"Bash\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>yum -y <span class=\"token function\">install</span> httpd <span class=\"token comment\"># 安装 Apache 组件</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>systemctl start httpd <span class=\"token comment\"># 启动 Apache 服务器</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>Apache 的配置文件的默认路径为： /etc/httpd/conf/httpd.conf</p>\n<p>网站默认存放的根目录： /var/www/html</p>\n<h3 id=\"步骤二-安装-php\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#步骤二-安装-php\">#</a> 步骤二： 安装 php</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><figcaption data-lang=\"Bash\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>yum -y <span class=\"token function\">install</span> php <span class=\"token comment\"># 安装 php 脚本语言</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>安装成功后，在 /var/www/html 下面创建 info.php 文件写入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight php\"><figcaption data-lang=\"PHP\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token function\">phpinfo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token delimiter important\">?&gt;</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><img data-src=\"phpinfo.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"步骤三-安装-mysql\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#步骤三-安装-mysql\">#</a> 步骤三 安装 mySQL</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><figcaption data-lang=\"Bash\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">wget</span> http://repo.mysql.com/mysql-community-release-el7-5.noarch.rpm</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">rpm</span> -ivh mysql-community-release-el7-5.noarch.rpm</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>yum -y <span class=\"token function\">install</span> mysql-server</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre>yum -y <span class=\"token function\">install</span> php-mysql</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre>systemctl start mysqld</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id=\"步骤四-配置mysql数据库并重启httpd\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#步骤四-配置mysql数据库并重启httpd\">#</a> 步骤四： 配置 MySQL 数据库，并重启 httpd</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><figcaption data-lang=\"Bash\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>mysql -u root -p <span class=\"token comment\">#不输入密码进入 Mysql</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">set</span> password <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token string\">'root'</span>@<span class=\"token string\">'localhost'</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>password<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'123456'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">#修改 root 用户密码</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>create database phpwind<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 创建数据库语法</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id=\"步骤五-网站搭建\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#步骤五-网站搭建\">#</a> 步骤五： 网站搭建</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><figcaption data-lang=\"Bash\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>https://down.chinaz.com/soft/27165.htm <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>gbk<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token comment\">#PHPWind 源代码下载位置</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>https://down.chinaz.com/soft/27521.htm <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>utf<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> </pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">chmod</span> -R <span class=\"token number\">777</span> /var/www/html/upload</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre>http://127.0.0.1/upload</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>在搭建的时候会遇到一些问题：这些问题是由于系统权限管理工具导致的</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><figcaption data-lang=\"Bash\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>setenforce <span class=\"token number\">0</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">#关闭防火墙</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>setenforce <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 开启防火墙</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id=\"lamp-一键部署\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#lamp-一键部署\">#</a> LAMP 一键部署</h2>\n<p>LAMP 一键安装脚本：<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubGFtcC5zaC8=\">https://www.lamp.sh/</span></p>\n<h3 id=\"步骤一-使用以下命令安装所需软件\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#步骤一-使用以下命令安装所需软件\">#</a> 步骤一： 使用以下命令安装所需软件</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><figcaption data-lang=\"Bash\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>yum -y <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token function\">wget</span> <span class=\"token function\">git</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id=\"步骤二-从远程仓库克隆到本地\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#步骤二-从远程仓库克隆到本地\">#</a> 步骤二： 从远程仓库克隆到本地</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><figcaption data-lang=\"Bash\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone https://github.com/teddysun/lamp.git</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> lamp</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">chmod</span> <span class=\"token number\">755</span> *.sh <span class=\"token comment\"># 赋予执行权限</span></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id=\"步骤三-开始安装\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#步骤三-开始安装\">#</a> 步骤三： 开始安装</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><figcaption data-lang=\"Bash\"></figcaption><table><tbody><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>./ lamp.sh</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>安装完成后注意，MySQL <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cDovL3huLS1sYW1wLTltOWc0NjRjZjQwYWVyYy5zaA==\">的密码是 lamp.sh</span></p>\n<h1 id=\"lnmp安装\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#lnmp安装\">#</a> LNMP 安装</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>L --&gt; linux【操作系统】</li>\n<li>N--&gt; Nginx 【中间件】</li>\n<li>M ---&gt; MySQL,MariaDB 【数据管理系统】</li>\n<li>P --&gt; PHP/Perl/Python 【脚本语言】</li>\n</ul>\n<p>LNMP 一键安装脚本：<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9sbm1wLm9yZy8=\">https://lnmp.org/</span></p>\n<h1 id=\"宝塔面板\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#宝塔面板\">#</a> 宝塔面板</h1>\n<p>安装教程： <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYnQuY24vYmJzL3RocmVhZC0xOTM3Ni0xLTEuaHRtbA==\">https://www.bt.cn/bbs/thread-19376-1-1.html</span></p>\n",
